Name: Server1 and Server2

AMI: Ubuntu

Instance type: t2.micro

Network:

VPC: DemoVPC

Subnet: Subnet1 or Subnet2

Enable Auto-assign Public IP

Security Group: Attach EC2-SG (and SSH-SG if needed)

In Advanced Details â†’ User data, paste:

